{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step inside the computer and join forces with your friend in <strong>Bytebond</strong>, an exhilarating co-op adventure where teamwork is the ultimate weapon. Explore multiple biomes, each teeming with new foes and mind-bending puzzles. Using your unique energy management abilities, collaborate with a friend in an online or classic split-screen environment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1952690/extras/gameplay.gif?t=1736777190\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1952690/extras/puzzles.png?t=1736777190\" /><strong>Dynamic Co-op Gameplay:</strong> Players collaborate to achieve common goals and overcome challenges together. Join forces to charge and convert energy, powering machines and solving puzzles to progress through levels. Don't have someone by your side? No worries; single-player mode is available too! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Challenges:</strong> Compete against a range of digital foes and virus bots while navigating difficult puzzles that need seamless teamwork and strategy. Adapt your techniques to defeat each individual adversary. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1952690/extras/cube.gif?t=1736777190\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1952690/extras/inside_pc.png?t=1736777190\" /><strong>Diverse Biomes</strong> - Traverse through different computer components, from the neon-lit circuits of the motherboard to the intricate pathways of the CPU. Each biome brings its unique set of enemies and puzzle challenges, keeping you on your toes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p